{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"544","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"有感嗎？主計總處：107年勞工年總報酬達73萬1,000元","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>2019-09-30 12:36<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>經濟日報 記者葉卉軒╱即時報導</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>主計總處今（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>30</span>）日發布<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>107</span>年事業人力僱用狀況調查統計顯示，受僱員工年齡逐年提高，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>45</span>歲以上者占了<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>32.9%</span>，比重持續擴大，且平均年齡增至<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>40.1</span>歲，較<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>106</span>年底增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>0.1</span>歲，續創新高，而逾六成為大專以上程度，在單一場所服務年資平均為<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>6.1</span>年，與<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>106</span>年持平。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>此外，在勞動報酬部份，主計處的最新調查發現，企業僱用員工時除給付薪資外，另須負擔勞保、健保、退休金提撥等非薪資報酬，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>107</span>年工業及服務業全年受僱員工每人非薪資報酬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>10</span>萬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2,000</span>元，加計薪資報酬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>62</span>萬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>9,000</span>元，總報酬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>73</span>萬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>1,000</span>元，較<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>106</span>年增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2</span>萬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>5,000</span>元或<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>3.6%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>其中，非薪資報酬增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>1,985</span>元或<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2.0%</span>，而薪資報酬中，經常性薪資增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>1</span>萬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2,372</span>元或<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2.6%</span>，非經常性薪資（包括加班費及非按月發放之工作、績效、全勤獎金、年節獎金等）增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>1</span>萬<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>752</span>元或<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>8.5%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>主計總處指出，此次調查的非經常性薪資占比為歷年最高，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>107</span>年受僱員工總報酬中經常性薪資、非 經常性薪資及雇主負擔之非薪資報酬所占比重分別為<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>67.2%</span>、<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>18.8%</span>、<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>14.0%,<span>&nbsp;</span></span>其中非經常性薪資所占比重為歷年最高，較<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>106</span>年增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>0.9</span>個百分點，主計總處表示，主要是<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>106</span>年景氣擴張，廠商於<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>107</span>年發放較多年終獎金及績效獎金所致。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>主計總處指出，受僱員工年齡確實逐年提高，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>107</span>年底工業及服務業受僱員工以<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>25</span>歲至<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>44</span>歲者占<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>58.2%</span>最多，但占比逐年下降，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>45</span>歲以上者占<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>32.9%</span>，較<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>6</span>年前增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>3.3</span>個百分點，平均年齡增至<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>40.1</span>歲，近六年增加<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>1.1</span>歲。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>此外，受高等教育普及影響，大專以上程度者占<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>63.2%</span>最多，且續呈上升。在單一場所之服務年資以<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>1</span>年至未滿三年者占<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>25.8%</span>最多，未滿<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>1</span>年、<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>5</span>年至未滿<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>10</span>年者均各占<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>18.5%</span>次之，平均服務年資<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>6.1</span>年，與<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>106</span>年持平。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>同時，主計總處調查還發現，因退休而離職者，隨勞保、勞退新制等實施漸近成熟期，以及人口高齡化等影響，屆齡退休人數漸增，近三年都超過<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>10</span>萬人，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>107</span>年退休人數達<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>10.1</span>萬人，較<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>106</span>年減少<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>3,000</span>人，占退出人次的<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>4.7%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 